data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the lovely Grand Oaks neighborhood of Houston. This magnificent residence offers 3 spacious bedrooms along with an oversized office and 2.5 baths. Step inside and be greeted by the tiled entry that stretches throughout all the main rooms while taking in the soaring ceilings and elegant archways to each wing of the home adding a touch of sophistication. The entire interior has been freshly painted and boasts new carpet. Situated on a desirable corner lot with an extended patio the backyard is the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings, relaxation, and creating lasting memories with friends and family. This is a prime location with easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and major highways. Enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities while still being able to retreat to your own serene oasis
